<item chapterid="605767" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1941" articlename="超级特卫传奇" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521801804" lastupdate="1521801804" chaptername="第580章流落孤岛" chapterorder="580" size="8354" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    这种卫星手机非常高端，水泡之后，放个七八个小时，自然而然就能恢复如常。

